# Windsurf Project Rules

Please read the `design_system.md` file located at the root of the project before generating or modifying any code in this repository. 
The design system contains all primary source-of-truth instructions on:
- Technology stack conventions (App Router, shadcn/ui, Tailwind).
- Reusable UI component rules.
- Color and typography usage as defined in the `tailwind.config.ts`.
- Code layout and dependency choices.

Any code you generate must strictly adhere to the guidelines set in `design_system.md`.
